    /     \       |  |         |     +---------+       無法互通
   ---------      |  +---------+                          ^
__/         \__   |    程式內的函式（不動程式碼無法分享） |
 |_    []   _|🕻---+  +------------------------------+     |
 |_   /||\  _|       |         +------------------+ |     |
 |_    /\   _|🕻------+ OpenAI  | Function calling | +-----+
---------------      | API     +------------------+ |
///////////////      +------------------------------+
</code></pre>
<h1 id="anthropic-制訂-mcp-要一統江湖">Anthropic 制訂 MCP
要一統江湖</h1>
<pre><code>                       MCP Host（與 LLM 溝通）   標準溝通方式   遠端/本機皆可
       o             +-----------------------+                 +-------------+
      / \            | Claude  +-----------+ |                 | MCP Server  |
     -----        +--+ ChatGPT | MCP client+-+🕻-+           +--+ Tools:      |
    /     \       |  |   ...   +-----------+ |  |  +-----+  |  | run cmd...  |
   ---------      |  +-----------------------+  |  |     |  |  +-------------+
__/         \__   |                             +--+ MCP +--+  ...  
 |_    []   _|🕻---+  +-----------------------+  |  |     |  |  +-------------+
 |_   /||\  _|       |         +-----------+ |  |  +-----+  |  | MCP Server  |
 |_    /\   _|🕻------+ LLM API | MCP client+-+🕻-+           +--+ Tools:      |
---------------      |         +-----------+ |                 | fetch web...|
///////////////      +-----------------------+                 +-------------+
</code></pre>
