   ---------      |  +--------|--------------+  |  |     |  |  +-------------+
__/         \__   |                             +--+ MCP +--+  ...  
 |_    []   _|🕻---+  +--------|--------------+  |  |     |  |  +-------------+
 |_   /||\  _|       |        |+-----------+ |  |  +-----+  |  | MCP Server  |
